reviews.text: Some might call The Varsity Club a campus bar oh, some might call it a campus area landmark, some may refer to it as their go-to location for OSU sport...
An OSU staple! Cozy, warm, communal, delicious fried food, and plenty of TVs to view the sport of your choosing. If you want to feel the spirit of legends...

Hey...for a campus bar
..not bad, devent food and reasonable prices. For a campus bar pretty clean....today. It may be different on a FOOTBALL Saturday!!!!
